      <title>乌克兰要求苹果、谷歌合作打击军事赌博</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-enlists-apple-google-in-military-gambling-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基已禁止该国军队内赌博，因为担心赌博会削弱士气并在对抗俄罗斯入侵的过程中构成安全风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-enlists-apple-google-in-military-gambling-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 10:20:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克以特斯拉义务为由推迟印度之行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/elon-musk-postpones-india-visit-to-later-in-the-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)推迟了对印度的访问，其中包括与总理纳伦德拉·莫迪(Narendra Modi)会面，称他必须解决特斯拉公司的紧迫问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/elon-musk-postpones-india-visit-to-later-in-the-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 04:53:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 猛烈抨击马斯克的“修正主义历史”，试图撤销诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/openai-slams-musk-s-revisionist-history-in-bid-to-toss-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 表示，埃隆·马斯克声称该公司为了追求利润而放弃了利他原则，这只不过是“修正主义历史”，也是为了提振其竞争对手的人工智能公司的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/openai-slams-musk-s-revisionist-history-in-bid-to-toss-lawsuit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 03:46:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的印度之行可能会为星链和特斯拉带来突破</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/musk-s-india-trip-to-see-breakthroughs-for-starlink-tesla</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在特斯拉公司进行有史以来最大规模的裁员几天后，距离发布季度财报仅几个小时，埃隆·马斯克将飞往印度，挤出时间与印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/musk-s-india-trip-to-see-breakthroughs-for-starlink-tesla</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 01:31:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币“减半”减少了对矿工构成威胁的新代币供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/bitcoin-halving-cuts-supply-of-new-tokens-in-threat-to-miners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[备受期待的比特币软件更新“减半”已经完成，这对那些通过确保数字货币平稳安全运行来赚钱的公司来说是一个潜在的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/bitcoin-halving-cuts-supply-of-new-tokens-in-threat-to-miners</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 00:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Netflix 的盈利和融资进度 |彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/netflix-s-earnings-and-ramp-s-fundraise-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者减少地缘政治担忧，彭博社的埃德·勒德洛 (Ed Ludlow) 带来了全面的市场报道。 Netflix 的收入前景令人失望，并计划停止报告其用户数量，股价下跌，金融服务平台 Ramp 又在新投资者 Khosla Ventures 的帮助下筹集了 1.5 亿美元，估值达到 76 亿美元。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/netflix-s-earnings-and-ramp-s-fundraise-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 21:54:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着油价上涨、电动汽车销售放缓，埃克森美孚市值超过特斯拉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/exxon-s-market-value-tops-tesla-s-as-oil-rises-ev-sales-slow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃克森美孚公司(Exxon Mobil Corp.)的市值一年多来首次超过特斯拉公司(Tesla Inc.)，此前这家电动汽车制造商的销售放缓，投资者押注消费者不愿放弃汽油动力汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/exxon-s-market-value-tops-tesla-s-as-oil-rises-ev-sales-slow</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 20:16:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股自 2022 年以来最大单周暴跌扰乱市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/tech-stocks-biggest-weekly-rout-since-2022-roils-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势和对利率前景的担忧，美国股市周五大幅抛售，导致科技股创下 17 个月来最大单周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/tech-stocks-biggest-weekly-rout-since-2022-roils-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 20:05:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能优胜者引领科技股抛售，超微和英伟达股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/super-micro-drops-near-two-month-low-on-earnings-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超微电脑公司和英伟达公司周五暴跌，这两家人工智能热门企业引领了广泛的科技股抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/super-micro-drops-near-two-month-low-on-earnings-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 14:47:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Netflix 因预测疲弱而下跌，并计划结束订阅人数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/netflix-adds-9-33-million-customers-crushing-street-forecasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，Netflix Inc. 股价创下两年来最大跌幅，原因是收入预测疲软，并且警告这家流媒体巨头将在 2025 年停止报告用户数量，这给今年原本强劲的开局蒙上了阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/netflix-adds-9-33-million-customers-crushing-street-forecasts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
